$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 SIT2 {
  coords 290.336 24.115 5705.007
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>PRELIMS</h2>"\
  "DTL: 24/07/2013, 1300hr, Al-Hadra, Iraq."\
  "Weather: Clear, no forecast of change, sightlines 1km+"\
  ""\
  "<h2>LORE</h2>"\
  "Large parts of Iraq have fallen into chaos as insurgent groups continue to seize territory across the region. Iraqi forces, weakened by years of fighting and heavy losses in both men and equipment, have struggled to contain the growing insurgency."\
  "North of Al-Hadra, a key highway checkpoint remains under Iraqi control, disrupting insurgent movement through the area. Intelligence reports indicate a large insurgent force is preparing to attack and eliminate the garrison stationed there in order to secure unrestricted access along the highway."\
  "The checkpoint is isolated and expected to come under heavy assault. Both sides understand the importance of the position — whoever controls the highway controls movement through the region."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 CS2 {
  coords 290.336 24.115 5705.007
  m_sTitle "Comsig"
  m_sTextData "<h2>CALLSIGNS</h2>"\
  "• HQ - Sharaf40"\
  "• 1st Squad - Sharaf41"\
  "• 2nd Squad - Sharaf42"\
  "• AT Team - Sharaf43"\
  "• Mortar team- Sharaf44"\
  ""\
  "<h2>FREQ/CHAN</h2>"\
  "• All callsigns - 48hz"\
  ""\
  "<h2>PASSWORDS</h2>"\
  "All can be changed at CO's discretion."\
  "• <b>Challenge:</b> Festive | <b>Password:</b> Cattle"\
  "• Running password: 22"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 EF2 {
  coords 290.336 24.115 5705.007
  m_sTitle "Enemy forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>  "\
  "Enemy forces consist of hardened Islamic insurgents.  "\
  "Estimated strength is approximately 70 personnel.  "\
  "Their current central location is unknown, though they are believed to be spread throughout Al-Hadra and staging for operations within the area.  "\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>  "\
  "• High morale - Following a string of victories, enemy morale remains high. Fighters are expected to engage aggressively and with little regard for casualties.  "\
  "• High mobility - The insurgents have access to a wide range of civilian and military vehicles, including BMPs, T-72/T-64/T-55 tanks, armed technicals, and captured Iraqi equipment such as M113s and Humvees.  "\
  "• Regularly known to employ VBIEDs and suicide bombers during assaults and defensive actions."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 FF2 {
  coords 290.336 24.115 5705.007
  m_sTitle "Friendly forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>  "\
  "We are Iraqi Army forces from 4th Platoon, Sharaf Company.  "\
  "Currently established within our fortified checkpoint north of Al-Hadra city, GRID:  038069"\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>  "\
  "• 2x .50 cal Humvees positioned along the highway at either end of the checkpoint.  "\
  "• Several static turrets covering the checkpoint perimeter.  "\
  "We have 1x Kornet ATGM with 3x missiles located in the eastern tower bunker, alongside various heavy and light machine guns positioned around the perimeter and on buildings. Reference map for exact locations.  "\
  "We can move these if we wish, but highly not recommend. Placement will be hard and the current postions are sighted."\
  "There is also an 82mm mortar with 40x HE, 25x Smokes, 15x Illum."\
  "• Our checkpoint contains multiple fortified fighting positions, with the ability to engage directly from the perimeter walls.  "\
  ""\
  "<h2>SERVICE & SUPPORT</h2>  "\
  "A supply crate is available inside the white building next to our starting position.  "\
  "It contains:  "\
  "• 6x PG-7VL | 2x TBG-7V | 3x OG-7V rockets.  "\
  "• 10x 100rnd PKM | 10x 100rnd M240 boxes.  "\
  "• Roughly 100x magazines across various rifles."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 MIS2 {
  coords 290.336 24.115 5705.007
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>MISSION STATEMENT</h2> "\
  "Our mission is to hold to the checkpoint at all costs and repel the imminent Insurgent attack."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRAQ"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
}